#a simple mapping for holding the wiimote vertically
#With only one hand on the wiimote, the uses here are 
#a bit limited.


assign wiimote up up
assign wiimote left left
assign wiimote right right
assign wiimote down down
assign wiimote a south
assign wiimote b east
assign wiimote 1 north
assign wiimote 2 west
assign wiimote plus start
assign wiimote home mode
assign wiimote minus select


#Tilt controls are mapped to a virtual left-stick,

enable wiimote accel
assign wiimote accelx left_x invert
assign wiimote accely left_y invert

#The IR sensor is mapped to a virtual right-stick.
#You'll probably want either tilt or IR, not both.

disable wiimote ir
assign wiimote ir_x right_x
assign wiimote ir_y right_y
